Package: thinnedDDP
Type: Package
Title: Fit the thinned dependent Dirichlet process via blocked Gibbs sampler
Version: 0.1
Date: 2026-05-21
Author: Laura D'Angelo
Maintainer: Laura D'Angelo <laura.dangelo@unimib.it>
Description: The package implements the blocked Gibbs sampler for fitting the thinned dependent Dirichlet process (thinned-DDP) of D'Angelo, Nipoti and Ongaro (2026, https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.18223) to grouped data.
